<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-22-0619 </DOCNO><TEXT>The article is a summary of a lecture on the desirability and acceptabilityof a nuclear power programme, presented by L.E.J. Roberts to the BritishEnergy Society and the Institution of Nuclear Engineers, 1987. The Sizewell-Bpublic inquiry and risks to health from radiation, natural backgroundradiation in the United Kingdom, reactor safety, and waste disposal,are all discussed. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>